gmcm.AnimalThrowKey.name: AnimalThrowKey
gmcm.AnimalThrowKey.tooltip: Hold this key when interacting with a farm animal to toss it instead of opening the animal query menu.
gmcm.AnimalBlocklist.name: AnimalBlocklist
gmcm.AnimalBlocklist.tooltip: Specify animal types (e.g. 'White Cow'), comma-separated, to prevent being able to toss animals of those types.
